net.morbz.osmonaut

Class IdTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.morbz.osmonaut.IdTracker

  • public class IdTracker
extends java.lang.Object
    Keeps track of which IDs are needed. Uses chunks of BitSet for storing IDs. Every ID requires at least 1 bit of memory + BitSet overhead. Doesn't support negative ID values.
